-- add-double.cell: minimal 2-cell test program (pure hard cells)
-- Tests: parse Ôćĺ find-ready Ôćĺ dispatch Ôćĺ oracle Ôćĺ decide Ôćĺ quiescence

ÔŐó add
  given a Ôëí 3
  given b Ôëí 5
  yield sum

  ÔŐó= sum ÔćÉ a + b

  ÔŐĘ sum = 8

ÔŐó double
  given addÔćĺsum
  yield result

  ÔŐó= result ÔćÉ addÔćĺsum * 2

  ÔŐĘ result = 16
